<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Chartify</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1 class="headhere">Chartify</h1>
    <div id="uniq">
      <form action="/chart" method="post">
        <label for="chartType">Type of Chart:</label>
        <input type="text" id="chartType" name="chartType" required />

        <label for="year">Year:</label>
        <input type="text" id="year" name="year" required />

        <label for="salary">That Year's Data:</label>
        <input type="text" id="yod" name="yod" required />

        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
      </form>
      <section class="lastpara">
        <h4>Usage Instruction</h4>
        <h6>
          1. Enter "Type of chart" as bar, pie, line : "Ex: pie" <br />
          2. Year should be in numbers separated by comma (,) : "Ex:
          2000,2010,2111..."<br />
          3. Year's Data is the data you want to see/compare for that year :
          "Ex: 7000,800,1900..."<br />
          4. After filling the form press submit and press back button to
          generate the new chart or modify details <br />
        </h6>
      </section>
    </div>
    <footer class="foot">Made with ❤️ by Anay</footer>
  </body>
</html>
